1 Engine Locking

- which version of node are we using
- create .nvmrc
  - lts/fermium = node 14
- create .npmrc
  - engine-strict=true
- specify enigines inside package.json
  "engines": {
  "node": ">=14.0.0",
  "yarn": ">=1.22.0",
  "npm": "please-use-yarn"
  },

