- add script

Git Hooks (Husky)

- script that runs on different stages of the git process to enforce code quality standards

1. git add .
2. git commit -m 'xxx'
3. git push

- yarn add -D husky
- npx husky install = creates .husky
- npx husky add .husky/pre-commit "yarn lint"
- npx husky add .husky/pre-push "yarn build"

